{"tid":300414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國務院列香港「販運人口第二級觀察名單」　港府轟不公平","createTime":"2017-06-28T01:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T11:30:16.000Z","uid":20933,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc737dd0b5feb50fd26ce2d6566849cf2ec60435","tid":300414,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170628/s00001/3a08b81cf947d6981b4c528e4b21ab61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170628%2Fs00001%2F3a08b81cf947d6981b4c528e4b21ab61.jpg&h=5fd54ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發表年度販運人口報告，繼續將香港列入第二級的觀察名單，指特區政府未能完全落實杜絕販運人口最低標準。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，過去一年港府只檢控五宗販賣人口個案，亦沒有全面將各種形式的販賣人口刑事化，只以較輕罪行檢控，當中只有三人因販運人口相關罪行被定罪判監超過一年。<br />\n<br />\n報告另指，特區政府沒有採取適當政策保障外傭免受剝削，也沒有就防止人口走私作色情活動提高公眾意識，決定將香港維持在第二級的監察名單。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府回應，強烈反對報告對香港的評級。發言人批評報告對部分香港打擊販賣人口工作有錯誤的描述及誤解，指結論不公平及偏頗，強調香港絕不姑息販運人口，又說「被識別的販運人口受害人數目相對較少，正好證實了販運人口的問題在香港並不普遍」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國務院報告將中國評級由去年的第二級觀察名單，降至最低的級別，與朝鮮、蘇丹、伊朗及敘利亞同級。報告指，中國未能達到阻止人口販運最低標準，情況未有重大改善。<br />\n<br />\n報告提到，中國有大批維吾爾人被強迫勞役，以及未經甄選之下強迫遣返朝鮮人回國。"},{"pid":"cc7f9b9a8fb0153eb47e6e20e5fa8f749e7729ac","tid":300414,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:21:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170628/s00001/1498609813255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170628%2Fs00001%2F1498609813255&d=AWFfUEWSyAy1hQVEKdBgyP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e4dd26e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170628%2Fs00001%2F1498609813255&h=93a7a456\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170628/s00001/1498609813255</a>"},{"pid":"d7af224dda7d187510a188a7956d1e006112e7a0","tid":300414,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780037ee983f35ad7b81b630c5922a780600665d","tid":300414,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:31:31.000Z","msg":"差佬都懶懶行係咁架啦"},{"pid":"68e730e03dcdd76464fabcac25dda0f7b1a779de","tid":300414,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:33:09.000Z","msg":"支那政府做乜干預人地美國國務院"},{"pid":"1c761a2b24d8ac04e4f8e6efcfc07d32c4445c78","tid":300414,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:52:27.000Z","msg":"另外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國國務院報告將中國評級由去年的第二級觀察名單，降至最低的級別，與朝鮮、蘇丹、伊朗及敘利亞同級</span></span>。"},{"pid":"868c46e19eeb73cee6372a7d4c6b3562e508458c","tid":300414,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759008ed6e29e0920750f0fea5918654815b22c2","tid":300414,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:56:04.000Z","msg":"咁比面唔係3級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846e807a30298fd64966d821a887667e01dc5ef5","tid":300414,"uid":25644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國國務院報告將中國評級由去年的第二級觀察名單，降至最低的級別，與朝鮮、蘇丹、伊朗及敘利亞同級</span></span>。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共享做中國人的榮耀"},{"pid":"d78d7d99b7d3b5ba2977142ed95eeba8c6f94b9b","tid":300414,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"黐親共產黨都唔慌有好野"},{"pid":"b071dc0de232d03b12f8fbc03af8fe6ac9ee10a6","tid":300414,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"即係之前通支那拐子佬黎香港拐細佬係真架啦"},{"pid":"d400ccd54f2d8ffa0d456fcf7672116ea09253a1","tid"